descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Seefeld wegfinder, the new mobility app of the Olympiaregion Seefeld!
With the Olympiaregion Seefeld’s new mobility app, you are sure to find the best way to get from A to B, whether by public transport, by bicycle, by car or on foot – Seefeld wegfinder will always find you the best and the quickest connection.

Route Planner & Stops
Seefeld wegfinder accesses all the public transport timetables and calculates the fastest route, including fares, from start to finish. GPS tracking allows routing to or from your current location and shows you all the bus & train stops in the area.

Up-to-date Departure Information
Up-to-date information about delays, technical issues, cancellations and platform changes is always available.

Mobility in the Olympiaregion Seefeld
As well as information about public transport, such as buses and trains, Seefeld wegfinder also provides you with an overview of other mobility possibilities in the region. Horse-drawn carriage rides to the most beautiful alpine pastures and huts, a tractor carriage ride through the nature park Karwendel or a segway ride along the valleys and meadows - all the options are clearly visible on the mobile map. Would you like to go on a mountain bike or e-bike ride? No problem - you can find the bike hire shops on Seefeld wegfinder too!

Clear Display
The Seefeld wegfinder online map shows you at a glance all the public transport stops, parking spaces, e-charging points, taxis & taxi stands, bike hire places, horse-drawn carriage stands, Segways, bikes, scooters, car-sharing options, and much more besides.

Save your favourite places & get to your destination faster
In order to get to your destination as quickly as possible, you can save your favourite places and most frequently-used routes as ‘Favourites‘ on Seefeld wegfinder.

Buy your Public Transport Ticket via the App
Save yourself a trip to the ticket counter or machine and buy your public transport ticket in ‘Chat‘ with just a few clicks. The ticket can be checked directly in the app or in your e-mail inbox.

Feedback
We are always looking for ways to improve Seefeld wegfinder. If you have any questions or comments, please feel free to contact us at any time at seefeld@wegfinder.at.

With the Olympiaregion Seefeld’s new mobility app, you are sure to find the best way to get from A to B, whether by public transport, by bicycle, by car or on foot – Seefeld wegfinder will always find you the best and the quickest connection.

Route Planner & Stops
Seefeld wegfinder accesses all the public transport timetables and calculates the fastest route, including fares, from start to finish. GPS tracking allows routing to or from your current location and shows you all the bus & train stops in the area.

Up-to-date Departure Information
Up-to-date information about delays, technical issues, cancellations and platform changes is always available.

Mobility in the Olympiaregion Seefeld
As well as information about public transport, such as buses and trains, Seefeld wegfinder also provides you with an overview of other mobility possibilities in the region. Horse-drawn carriage rides to the most beautiful alpine pastures and huts, a tractor carriage ride through the nature park Karwendel or a segway ride along the valleys and meadows - all the options are clearly visible on the mobile map. Would you like to go on a mountain bike or e-bike ride? No problem - you can find the bike hire shops on Seefeld wegfinder too!

Clear Display
The Seefeld wegfinder online map shows you at a glance all the public transport stops, parking spaces, e-charging points, taxis & taxi stands, bike hire places, horse-drawn carriage stands, Segways, bikes, scooters, car-sharing options, and much more besides.

Save your favourite places & get to your destination faster
In order to get to your destination as quickly as possible, you can save your favourite places and most frequently-used routes as ‘Favourites‘ on Seefeld wegfinder.

Buy your Public Transport Ticket via the App
Save yourself a trip to the ticket counter or machine and buy your public transport ticket in ‘Chat‘ with just a few clicks. The ticket can be checked directly in the app or in your e-mail inbox.

Feedback
We are always looking for ways to improve Seefeld wegfinder. If you have any questions or comments, please feel free to contact us at any time at seefeld@wegfinder.at.
